  <product-descriptor code="PBEARDEDTHEME" release-date="20260203" release-version="11" optional="true"/>

  <description><![CDATA[
    <h2>Bearded Theme for IntelliJ</h2>
    <p>A carefully crafted collection of <b>64 color themes</b> for JetBrains IDEs,
    ported from the popular VS Code extension by BeardedBear.</p>

    <h3>Theme Families</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Classics</b> — Anthracite (dark) and Light</li>
      <li><b>Arc</b> — Arc, Eolstorm, Blueberry, Eggplant, Reversed</li>
      <li><b>Vivid</b> — Purple, Black, Light</li>
      <li><b>Monokai</b> — Terra, Metallian, Stone, Black, Reversed</li>
      <li><b>Solarized</b> — Dark, Reversed, Light</li>
      <li><b>Oceanic</b> — Oceanic, Reversed</li>
      <li><b>Milkshake</b> — Raspberry, Blueberry, Mango, Mint, Vanilla</li>
      <li><b>Black &amp; Gems</b> — Gold, Ruby, Emerald, Diamond, Amethyst (+ Soft variants)</li>
      <li><b>Aquarelle</b> — Cymbidium, Hydrangea, Lilac</li>
      <li><b>High Contrast</b> — Ebony, Midnight Void, Wonderland Wood, Brewing Storm, Flurry</li>
      <li><b>Stained</b> — Purple, Blue</li>
      <li><b>Surprising</b> — Eggplant, Blueberry, Watermelon</li>
      <li><b>Exotic</b> — Earth, Coffee, Coffee Cream, Voided, Altica</li>
      <li><b>Featured</b> — Will, Gold D Raynh, Melle Julie, WebDevCody</li>
      <li><b>Special</b> — Colorblind, OLED, Minuit, Chocolate Espresso</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Includes</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Full UI theming (tool windows, tabs, trees, menus, buttons, etc.)</li>
      <li>Complete editor color schemes with language-specific highlighting</li>
      <li>Bearded Icons file icon set</li>
      <li>Support for Java, Kotlin, Python, JavaScript/TypeScript, Go, Rust, PHP, HTML/CSS, JSON, YAML, Markdown, and more</li>
    </ul>

    <p><em>A subscription of $1/month supports continued development and theme updates.</em></p>
  ]]></description>

  <change-notes><![CDATA[
    <h3>1.0.0</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Initial release with 64 theme variants</li>
      <li>Bearded Icons file icon set</li>
      <li>Full editor color scheme support</li>
      <li>Language-specific syntax highlighting for 12+ languages</li>
    </ul>
  ]]></change-notes>

